snippet.title: BABY! - Seishun Buta Yarou wa Bunny Girl Senpai no Yume wo Minai Episode 10 Insert Song [Synthesia]
snippet.description:
BABY! from Seishun Buta Yarou, Episode 10! The scene was so cute~

As soon as I saw the full version (props to NattoChan ネル for releasing it so fast) I knew I had to arrange the song. And so I did. 

You know, anime doesn't get much better than this. 

P.S. I have started trying Soundcloud for audio, tell me what you think! 
P.P.S I have a Discord server now! Feel free to join!
